                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-213-victim1887 t18300415-213-viclabel1182"></join>. On the 17th of April I was going from <placeName id="t18300415-213-crimeloc1183">Wimpole-street to Oxford-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-213-crimeloc1183" type="placeName" value="Wimpole-street to Oxford-street"></interp>
